public static class MockCatalogReader.MustFilterMockTable extends MockCatalogReader.MockTable implements SemanticTable
Mock implementation of MockCatalogReader.MockTable that supports must-filter fields.

Must-filter fields are declared via methods in the SemanticTable interface.
